### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8010/health

### Run one SKU (force)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8010/mc/sku/M524-100L
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "n_sims": 8000,
  "review_days": 30,
  "force": true
}

### Batch run (prioridad alta primero)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8010/mc/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "n_sims": 8000,
  "review_days": 30,
  "min_priority": 8
}

### Cache
GET http://127.0.0.1:8010/mc/cache/M524-100L
